summary:
Mumargi" Sketchbook & Digitial, 2018
It's been a while since I've dabbled with any Pokemon and since Mismagius is my favorite...
body:
Mumargi" Sketchbook & Digitial, 2018

It’s been a while since I’ve dabbled with any Pokemon and since Mismagius is my favorite witchy-looking ghost type, I figured I’d try my rendition of it for the month :)

It’s always such an odd transition for me switching from long periods of only doing linework into colors. I really enjoyed how the subtle glow turned out on this though. Not bad for being a few months out of practice, heh

summary: Mewtwo's Voice Actor is ALIVE! - Did You Know Voice Acting? extra (feat. Nowacking) Did you know that the original voice actor...
caption:
Mewtwo’s Voice Actor is ALIVE! - Did You Know Voice Acting? extra (feat. Nowacking)

Did you know that the original voice actor for Mewtwo in Pokemon: The First Movie was actually a successful Broadway actor? For many years, an unfortunate mix-up led many fans of his performance to think Mewtwo’s legendary first voice had passed away, but this video details the story of his experience on the hit Anime franchise, his departure from it and how the mistake happened in the first place! Plus, the famous 150th Pokemon actually has many OTHER legendary voices you might be surprised to learn some interesting facts about!

Originally inspired by “Did You Know Gaming?”

summary:
Candevee Floss Eevee and Candy Floss fusion Nutritional Information: Sugar Type Ability: Cotton Candy: 

Halves the damage taken...
caption:
Candevee Floss

Eevee and Candy Floss fusion

Nutritional Information:

Sugar Type

Ability: Cotton Candy:  Halves the damage taken from moves that make direct contact, but doubles that of Drink Type moves.

Signature Move: Sticky Coat - The user is protected by their sugary coat and the opponent get stuck to their coat.  This move protects the user and lowers the speed of the opponent if the move they use makes direct contact.

The Sweet Fluff Pokemon

Candevee Floss is a ball of fun and loves to waft it sweet scent around for everyone to smell. It can be very sticky to hold and many trainers have found that their Candevee Floss is very hard to remove.  It doesn’t like being grabbed by its wooden tail.

Day 6 of the Hallowee Event and we have a Candy Floss/Cotton Candy Eevee suggested by @littlemoonbunny. I decided to make Eevee a ball of fluff because that’s pretty much what Candy Floss/Cotton Candy is. I absolutely love the pastel pinks and blues and purples you can find in Candy Floss/Cotton Candy.
